ailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/16\/heart-no-quran-ruined-bayt\/","url_meta":{"origin":3375,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Heart without the Book like ruined house","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 16, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, one who does not hold anything from the Quran within himself is like a ruined house.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2913 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38653,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/01\/26\/taleem-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":3375,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Teaching: Best Muslims teach Quran they have learned","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 26, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best of you are those who learn the Quran and teach it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2909 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0637\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0628\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25022,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/13\/ask-allah-by-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":3375,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Ask only from Allah with the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 13, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"'Imran ibn Husayn reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever reads the Quran, let him ask Allah by it. Verily, people will come who recite the Quran and ask people by it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2917 Grade: Sahih li ghayri (authentic due to external\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17436,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/01\/prophet-recite-quran-nawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":3375,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Quran: The Prophet recites Quran before sleep","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 1, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would not sleep in his bed until he has recited Surat Bani Isra\u2019il and Al-Zumar. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2920 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u06